Charles Brinley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Brinley 0 Charles Brinley (November 15, 1880 – February 17, 1946) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 140 films between 1913 and 1939. He was born in Yuma, Arizona and died in Los Angeles, California.
